01:10:37,433 --> 01:10:39,335
lies the mystery of tefillah.

766
01:10:39,768 --> 01:10:40,936
What is tefillah?

767
01:10:40,936 --> 01:10:44,406
I can open the door and walk in
and appear -- and appear before the

768
01:10:44,406 --> 01:10:49,545
throne of the Almighty and complain
and to cry and to thank, 

769
01:10:49,545 --> 01:10:52,681
 and to demand and to request and to beg. 

770
01:10:56,118 --> 01:11:04,493
In a word, man who aspires
to kingship must open up

771
01:11:04,493 --> 01:11:12,468
his existence, be communicative,
accessible, and be capable of coordinating

772
01:11:12,935 --> 01:11:16,338
his basic needs with the needs of others.

773
01:11:18,173 --> 01:11:19,475
When I say

774
01:11:19,475 --> 01:11:23,912
an open existence, please
don't make any mistake.

775
01:11:23,912 --> 01:11:28,684
I do not mean the cultivation of
sociability or gregariousness.

776
01:11:30,986 --> 01:11:37,726
An open existence can be achieved
by the introvert or even the

777
01:11:37,726 --> 01:11:40,129
introspective person nowadays.

778
01:11:43,132 --> 01:11:48,370
Sociability, gregariousness are
not necessarily the traits

779
01:11:48,904 --> 01:11:51,940
of an -- of existential openness.

780
01:11:53,142 --> 01:11:53,842
What I

781
01:11:53,842 --> 01:11:59,515
want to express with
this term is that man,

782
01:12:02,217 --> 01:12:11,360
while living, working, suffering,
rejoicing, and moving along an endless

783
01:12:11,360 --> 01:12:18,367
trail of his own which no one else
will ever cross, must always remember

784
01:12:19,268 --> 01:12:26,108
that in spite of the fact that he
is a singular being, he is not the

785
01:12:26,108 --> 01:12:29,912
only one and he's not a single being.

786
01:12:31,113 --> 01:12:37,953
That God's concern encompasses
not only him, but countless

787
01:12:37,953 --> 01:12:45,361
individuals like him who also
wander, each one along his own trail.

788
01:12:48,397 --> 01:12:53,302
 While malchus in general historical terms

789
01:12:56,438 --> 01:13:01,043
precipitates separation of the king from the people, 

790
01:13:01,043 --> 01:13:07,483
 his elevation over them and his existential exquisiteness, 

791
01:13:08,917 --> 01:13:12,688
 by moving the king from the periphery, 

792
01:13:12,688 --> 01:13:16,458
 from the crowd, to the center,  

