01:17:52,768 --> 01:17:57,139
agony, and hope,

855
01:17:57,673 --> 01:18:01,677
I turn from rei'a into what?

856
01:18:02,310 --> 01:18:04,046
Into what?

857
01:18:04,446 --> 01:18:05,580
Into a brother.

858
01:18:05,580 --> 01:18:07,149
Into ach.

859
01:18:09,317 --> 01:18:19,695
This higher degree of coexistence, of
interrelatedness and, and companionship.

860
01:18:26,068 --> 01:18:28,036
A brother, 

