862
01:18:32,407 --> 01:18:34,476
Existential unity.

863
01:18:35,977 --> 01:18:37,479
One destiny.

864
01:18:38,580 --> 01:18:39,781
One life.

865
01:18:40,048 --> 01:18:41,349
One memory.

