01:34:42,610 --> 01:34:44,045
He's a very poor teacher.

1050
01:34:44,045 --> 01:34:46,781
I wouldn't hire him as a rosh yeshiva 
if I were the boss.

1051
01:34:54,855 --> 01:34:59,393
It consists in the metaphysical,
or I would say, metapersonal

1052
01:35:00,327 --> 01:35:08,736
process or gesture of opening up
one's existence, of letting the

1053
01:35:08,736 --> 01:35:17,378
student share in the great spiritual
treasures stored up in the depths

1054
01:35:17,978 --> 01:35:20,014
and the recesses of the teacher.

1055
01:35:22,149 --> 01:35:28,122
One cannot teach unless he tears down
old barriers, separating individual

1056
01:35:28,723 --> 01:35:30,958
