1088
01:38:05,980 --> 01:38:07,848
all nations will come to hear him.

1089
01:38:08,215 --> 01:38:13,087
As it is said, "And at the end of
days, it shall come to pass that

1090
01:38:13,087 --> 01:38:17,157
the mount of the Lord's house
shall be established -- established

1091
01:38:17,625 --> 01:38:19,827
at the top of the mountain. And

1092
01:38:19,827 --> 01:38:24,298
we taught of His ways and we'll -- and
