1134
01:41:54,108 --> 01:41:57,211
What happens to the person
who achieves kingship?

1135
01:41:58,312 --> 01:42:08,288
A closed-up sensing, self-oriented
-- ego-conscious and within-minded

1136
01:42:08,288 --> 01:42:14,495
individual opens up toward the
outside, tears down old fences,

1137
01:42:15,395 --> 01:42:21,101
orientations, trends, it'll be a
gesture of magnanimity, spreads out

1138
